        "usually singular; means need or demand"
      ],
      "collocations": [
        {
          "text": "bei Bedarf",
          "meaning": "if needed"
        },
        {
          "text": "den Bedarf ermitteln",
          "meaning": "to determine the need"
        }
      ],
      "wordFamilies": [
        {
          "lemma": "bedürfen",
